  "prompt": "Which are the best IELTS coaching institutes in Delhi?",
  "response": "There are several reputable IELTS coaching institutes in Delhi known for their effective teaching methods and high success rates. Here are some of the best ones:\n\n1. **British Council**: As one of the co-creators of the IELTS, the British Council offers comprehensive coaching programs and resources, along with a deep understanding of the test structure.\n\n2. **IDP Education**: Another co-owner of the IELTS, IDP provides a range of preparatory courses, including personalized coaching and practice tests.\n\n3. **Kaplan International**: Known for its global presence, Kaplan offers structured courses and extensive practice materials tailored for IELTS preparation.\n\n4. **Manya Group**: This institute provides specialized courses for IELTS preparation, along with extensive support and resources for students.\n\n5. **EduCere**: Offers personalized coaching and focuses on developing language skills and test strategies tailored to each student.\n\n6. **Lakshya**: Known for its result-oriented teaching approach, Lakshya provides comprehensive IELTS coaching with experienced faculty.\n\n7. **RBS Online IELTS Coaching**: Offers flexible online coaching courses with live classes, which can be a convenient option for many students.\n\n8. **Apex IELTS Institute**: They offer customized batches and focus on building the necessary skills for the test.\n\n9. **MINDMINE**: Known for its rigorous training and mock tests, MINDMINE helps students develop their language skills alongside test strategies.\n\n10. **Chase Success**: Offers intensive coaching programs and focuses on helping students achieve high scores in IELTS.\n\nBefore enrolling, it's a good idea to visit these institutes, talk to faculty, and check reviews and success stories from former students to find the best fit for your learning style and needs.",
